item.title: About Me
item.description: About Hey there, welcome to my site, I’m a rugby player who plays for the Austin Huns and who happens to be a developer as well. I’m a rubyist but I also really like Go lang. I am not afraid of being a full stack developer and I am open to contributing to anything just click the little mail icon and reach out to me with any opportunities! I’ve written some books and they can be found here!
